{"tid":1003770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大部分醫療資源，都係用係最年老果批人度","createTime":"2019-02-01T02:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T10:59:59.000Z","uid":137220,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4df53588d2debc2e817f0414856f0e319f2382e6","tid":1003770,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:37:49.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1003452/page/5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1003452/page/5</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\nhk01係奶共，我知<br />\n每日150都絕對應該削<br />\n<br />\n但咁都代表所有醫療問題都係佢地做成<br />\n現實係醫療資源大部份係年老人用，果班人大部份都未去到咁老<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當然再過多10年20年，當佢地老，問題都會出現<br />\n所以每日150，係絕對要解決</span><br />\n有醫生話要cut每日150，連登仔讚好，我都贊成<br />\n<br />\n但係，<span style=\"color: red;\">現時ge問題</span>，主要都係因為政府無擺足夠資源姐<br />\neg.人口增加，床位減少，病人:醫護比例高，醫管局管理無效率/廢<br />\n<br />\n要將依家呢個醫療資源不足問題，全歸咎比每日150，係無助解決現時問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都有research講過7-8成醫療資源，都係用係最年老果批人度<br />\n尤其是係臨死果幾年<br />\n<br />\n所以 &quot;每日150並非造成現時醫療資源不足&quot; 呢個論點係錯唔曬<br />\n你睇下你識ge人入面，都知大部份人係4-5十歲先開始有長期病<br />\n普通後生點會用到醫院?"},{"pid":"5f51147ef6da9521b45f9797d733aac53e8a3a8c","tid":1003770,"uid":75326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"立法安樂死?"},{"pid":"8049a2fdf1b667ca7eb4d590ef3326a935b07f93","tid":1003770,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f51147ef6da9521b45f9797d733aac53e8a3a8c","tid":1003770,"uid":75326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"立法安樂死?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"電影推介<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/imagecache/w456/column_images/TPA_poster_ref_1408416121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2Fw456%2Fcolumn_images%2FTPA_poster_ref_1408416121.jpg&h=f97f4434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56acba55d6a37876277b632e85be7f1379b7634c","tid":1003770,"uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"我用一個住老人院ge老人做例子:<br />\n<br />\n生活不能自理，用傷殘津貼住老人院 ($7-8000/month，一年$96,000)<br />\n每3個月覆診 (每次政府普通科門診$445元，一年$1780，其實佢地食勁多藥，不過藥錢難計)<br />\n<br />\n每兩個月入急症室一次(急症室每次診症$1,230，一年$7380)<br />\n再入院5日 (住院費用 (普通科醫院)\t每天$5,100元，一年$150,300)<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://www.ha.org.hk/visitor/fees_and_charges.asp?lang=CHIB5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha.org.hk%2Fvisitor%2Ffees_and_charges.asp%3Flang%3DCHIB5&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=8226f5dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ha.org.hk/visitor/fees_and_charges.asp?lang=CHIB5</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n入過醫院/去過老人院/行內人就知我無吹水"},{"pid":"d21d3024c756a3c46d8d8357981676d311ac23c2","tid":1003770,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f51147ef6da9521b45f9797d733aac53e8a3a8c","tid":1003770,"uid":75326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"立法安樂死?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:51:12.000Z","msg":"我絕對贊成呀師兄"},{"pid":"2d0e58eda4e3806f87af0c4e330631d20c54744d","tid":1003770,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"我意思係，將個焦點擺落去 &quot;cut每日150&quot; 呢個將近無可能做到ge事<br />\n亦唔係現時問題重心<br />\n<br />\n係解決唔到依家問題"},{"pid":"487e4a7dce4f2b81af414acc10df4f4f52724e52","tid":1003770,"uid":17616,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:54:32.000Z","msg":"想轉移視線？收皮啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n停150隻蟲同爭取投放資源無衝突可以同時進行架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3aad7c1c7138171deab44d9726b0db31a52ffb","tid":1003770,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"487e4a7dce4f2b81af414acc10df4f4f52724e52","tid":1003770,"uid":17616,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:54:32.000Z","msg":"想轉移視線？收皮啦你<